    "course_title": "DIGITAL MEDIA AND SCIENCE COMMUNICATION",
    "description": "Explores how to navigate the complex world of digital and networked communication tools with an eye toward a wide variety of careers in communication. Understand and evaluate social implications of digital media, informed by the most recent scholarship and classical theories. Attention is given to implications for public engagement with controversial scientific issues.",
